Silence::

She looked up at him, glad to see that she wasn't going to be shot
where she stood. "I am the one to whom two bots were sent to find. It
was my pod that sent the signal that was responded to. I am Silence."

She stood before him.  Her wings were fold behind her short, slender,
white and gold frame.  Her large owl optics looked at him apprisingly.
She guested he must have been either a leader or high up in the
security ranks. Her soft spoken voice and demeaner were classic
characteristics of the animal that she changed into. (Barn Owl).  Her
head tilted to one side slight, "And what is the name by which you are
called?"
